NAME
	CI5CO WLC Banhammer 

SYNOPSIS
	./wlcban

DESCRIPTION
	The CI5CO WLC Banhammer was created to provide a fast and simple way to ban 
	users across multiple wireless lan controllers. This tool takes an input of 
	MAC addresses and a comment, adding, or removing addresses to the diabled 
	clients list. 

	The script needs to be customized for individual enviornments so please take 
	time to look at the code. 

